---
layout: default
title: "Index"
description: "Studio Upleft"

bg-default: "#202C19"
bg-muted: "#151D11"
text-default: "#E5EEE0"
text-muted: "#A1B69A"
text-interactive: "#E5EEE0"
border-default: "#E5EEE0"
border-muted: "rgba(255, 255, 255, .25)"
---
<div class="hero">
  <h1 class="self-end mb-2">System-minded visual design and brand-friendly product design for your next project.</h1>
</div>
<div class="pb-2 md:pb-4">
  <p class="text-muted">Recent Work</p>
</div>
<ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-8 md:gap-y-12">
{%- for featured in collections.featured reversed -%}
  <li>
    <a href="{{ featured.url }}" class="no-underline hover:opacity-90">
      <div class="aspect-video bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('{{ featured.url }}{{ featured.data.image }}'); background-color: {{ featured.data.bg-default }};"></div>
      <p class="leading-tight mt-4">{{ featured.data.title-short }}</p>
      <p class="text-muted uppercase text-xs mt-1">{{ featured.data.role }}</p>
    </a>
  </li>
{%- endfor -%}
</ul>


<ul class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 gap-x-2 sm:gap-x-4 gap-y-8 md:gap-y-12 mt-12 sm:mt-16">
{%- for published in collections.published reversed -%}
  <li>
    <a href="{{ published.url }}" class="no-underline hover:opacity-90">
      <div class="aspect-square bg-cover bg-center mb-2" style="background-image: url('{{ published.url }}/{{ published.data.image }}'); background-color: {{ published.data.bg-default }};"></div>
      <p class="leading-tight mt-4">{{ published.data.title-short }}</p>
      <p class="text-muted uppercase text-xs mt-1">{{ published.data.role }}</p>
    </a>
  </li>
{%- endfor -%}
</ul>
